V4a
http://www.fpsbanana.com/maps/9115

Well that didnt take long, this should be the final one :)
btw i use phys_pushscale -1000 when i play this map (its more fun)

fixed the hostage nav
added an elevator to the end (if your a lazy one that doesnt like jumping)
got rid of custom textures
changed the wall texture to something a bit more light
town looks nicer now
added some explosions when you shoot the glass targets
removed the two hostages from spawn, but left the area (added a bomb button for the area incase someones spawn killing) and a button to blow up the cars
added camera props so you know where the cameras are
